items.name: Auxium
explicitMods: Chill Effect and Freeze Duration on you are based on 65% of Energy Shield
19% increased Elemental Damage with Attack Skills
0.2% of Attack Damage Leeched as Mana per Power Charge
flavourText: As long as the soul is unfettered, so is the body.

items.name: Thief's Torment
explicitMods: Gain 24 Life per Enemy Hit with Attacks
Gain 15 Mana per Enemy Hit with Attacks
50% reduced Effect of Curses on you
flavourText: The ring I stole,
My finger they took,
A shrouded mind,
Cut their curses short,
As I drained their spirit
And stole their soul.
A blessing is often a curse.

items.name: Reverberation Rod
explicitMods: Socketed Gems are Supported by Level 10 Spell Echo
flavourText: If it's worth doing once, it's worth doing twice.

items.name: Rotgut
explicitMods: 15% chance to gain a Flask Charge when you deal a Critical Strike
Gain Onslaught for 1 second per Frenzy Charge on use
items.descrText: Right click to drink. Can only hold charges while in belt. Refills as you kill monsters.
flavourText: Rancid, rotten, and wicked are those that dare to taste my serum.

items.name: Doedre's Tenure
flavourText: While Doedre lacked Maligaro's sense of style,
she surpassed her master in pure malevolence.

items.name: Ungil's Gauche
explicitMods: +12% Chance to Block Attack Damage while Dual Wielding
flavourText: Unwieldy and garish became graceful
and deadly in Ungil's nimble hands.

items.name: Mindspiral
explicitMods: Enemies Cannot Leech Mana From you
8% of Damage taken Recouped as Mana
flavourText: Where top is bottom and weak is strong.

items.name: Bramblejack
explicitMods: Adds 2 to 4 Physical Damage to Attacks
-2 Physical Damage taken from Attack Hits
40% of Melee Physical Damage taken reflected to Attacker
flavourText: It is safer to be feared than to be loved.

items.name: Belt of the Deceiver
explicitMods: 10% reduced Chance to Block Attack and Spell Damage
You take 30% reduced Extra Damage from Critical Strikes
flavourText: In battle, virtue matters not.
Only victory.

items.name: Shiversting
explicitMods: 0.6% of Physical Attack Damage Leeched as Mana
flavourText: Stoic visage, icy heart.
Life of sorrow, lived apart.

items.name: Dyadus
explicitMods: Adds 187 to 216 Fire Damage in Main Hand
Adds 179 to 214 Cold Damage in Off Hand
25% chance to Ignite when in Main Hand
100% increased Chill Duration on Enemies when in Off Hand
40% increased Damage with Ignite inflicted on Chilled Enemies
flavourText: Born of love, forged in blood
He burned as a torch in the blackest night
She shone as ice in the winter sun
Proudly, fiercely
At their mother's side, forever.

items.name: Ondar's Clasp
explicitMods: 30% increased Attack Speed when on Full Life
Adds 1 to 13 Lightning Damage to Attacks
20% increased Movement Speed when on Low Life
flavourText: A single lightning strike fells a man.
A single knife stroke fells an empire.

items.name: Malachai's Artifice
explicitMods: +91% to Fire Resistance when Socketed with a Red Gem
+86% to Cold Resistance when Socketed with a Green Gem
+94% to Lightning Resistance when Socketed with a Blue Gem
flavourText: When the wind blows,
Know which way to bend
and watch the others break.

implicitMods: 4% chance to Freeze, Shock and Ignite
flavourText: The wolf greeted the king,
In the light of the harvest moon.
The wolf offered the strength of the wild,
And the king paid for it in blood.

items.name: Snakebite
explicitMods: 2% increased Attack Speed per Frenzy Charge
6% increased Accuracy Rating per Frenzy Charge
10% reduced Frenzy Charge Duration per Frenzy Charge
While at maximum Frenzy Charges, Attacks Poison Enemies
flavourText: "As the serpent shuns thought,
It shuns fear.
It strikes with the speed of wrath
And the skill of compulsion."
- Deshret, The Red Sekhema

items.name: Rigwald's Crest
explicitMods: Trigger Level 10 Summon Spectral Wolf on Kill
flavourText: Within the heart of every man and woman
lies the soul of a ferocious beast.
If you cannot tame it, embrace it.

items.name: Reaper's Pursuit
explicitMods: 15% increased Movement Speed when on Full Life
flavourText: Accept your fate, or lie, pretend.
Death collects you in the end.

items.name: Sundance
flavourText: Blazing body, shining bold.
Dance beneath the orb of gold!

items.name: Ming's Heart
explicitMods: Gain 20% of Physical Damage as Extra Chaos Damage
flavourText: Ming slew Tranquillity
Took Chaos for his wife
And on Her immortal finger
He placed his Heart

items.name: The Peregrine
explicitMods: 0.2% of Attack Damage Leeched as Mana
flavourText: We wander to pass time.
We travel to fulfill.

items.name: Kaltenhalt
explicitMods: Reflects 30 Cold Damage to Melee Attackers
flavourText: Cold, miserable and alone... but alive.

items.name: Last Resort
explicitMods: 25% increased Attack Speed when on Low Life
100% increased Claw Physical Damage when on Low Life
100% increased Accuracy Rating when on Low Life
flavourText: Desperate times demand desperate measures.

items.name: Honourhome
explicitMods: Adds 1 to 13 Lightning Damage to Spells and Attacks
+20% to all Elemental Resistances while on Low Life
20% reduced Mana Cost of Skills when on Low Life
flavourText: "The craven mind is sharp with self interest.
The honourable mind is much easier to manipulate."
- Malachai the Soulless

items.name: Bitterdream
explicitMods: Socketed Gems are Supported by Level 1 Hypothermia
Socketed Gems are Supported by Level 1 Ice Bite
Socketed Gems are Supported by Level 1 Cold Penetration
Socketed Gems are Supported by Level 1 Mana Leech
Socketed Gems are Supported by Level 10 Added Cold Damage
Socketed Gems are Supported by Level 1 Inspiration
flavourText: Fight not the cold
Forsake hope
Be still.

items.name: Redbeak
explicitMods: 100% increased Damage when on Low Life
flavourText: As battle calms, blood turns to rust.

items.name: Wurm's Molt
explicitMods: 0.4% of Physical Attack Damage Leeched as Life
0.4% of Physical Attack Damage Leeched as Mana
flavourText: They say a lifetime of wisdom is carried
in every skin the great beasts shed.

items.name: Last Resort
explicitMods: 25% increased Attack Speed when on Low Life
100% increased Claw Physical Damage when on Low Life
100% increased Accuracy Rating when on Low Life
flavourText: Desperate times demand desperate measures.

items.name: Thousand Teeth Temu
explicitMods: 0.4% of Physical Attack Damage Leeched as Life
Reflects 1 to 1000 Physical Damage to Attackers on Block
flavourText: Crimson burn'd the star of sadness,
All was woe that seem'd but gladness.

items.name: Sin Trek
explicitMods: Enemies Cannot Leech Life From you
flavourText: Do not let them step on your feet. Keep them at bay.

items.name: Bloodboil
explicitMods: Adds 9 to 20 Fire Damage to Attacks
45% reduced Effect of Chill on you
flavourText: Rage is a big part of courage.

items.name: Cloak of Flame
explicitMods: Reflects 15 Fire Damage to Melee Attackers
20% of Physical Damage from Hits taken as Fire Damage
flavourText: He who sows an ember shall reap an inferno.

items.name: Rotgut
explicitMods: 15% chance to gain a Flask Charge when you deal a Critical Strike
Gain Onslaught for 1 second per Frenzy Charge on use
items.descrText: Right click to drink. Can only hold charges while in belt. Refills as you kill monsters.
flavourText: Rancid, rotten, and wicked are those that dare to taste my serum.

items.name: Sidhebreath
explicitMods: 0.2% of Physical Attack Damage Leeched as Mana
flavourText: The breath of life is yours to give.

items.name: Realmshaper
implicitMods: +12% Chance to Block Attack Damage while wielding a Staff
explicitMods: +1 to Level of Socketed Fire Gems
+1 to Level of Socketed Cold Gems
Socketed Gems are Supported by Level 5 Cold to Fire
flavourText: "God's creations always begin and end
with flames and ice.
We should count ourselves lucky when we see neither."
- Archbishop Geofri

items.name: Tremor Rod
implicitMods: +12% Chance to Block Attack Damage while wielding a Staff
explicitMods: Socketed Gems are Supported by Level 10 Blastchain Mine
Mines can be Detonated an additional time
flavourText: The best way to gain the element of surprise,
is to let your enemy learn your plans,
and execute them - twice.

items.name: Voidhome
explicitMods: 0.4% of Physical Attack Damage Leeched as Mana
flavourText: Cursed is the star whence it came.

items.name: Carcass Jack
flavourText: "...The discomfort shown by the others is amusing, but none
can deny that my work has made quite the splash..."
- Maligaro's Journal
